  "title": "Delivery Rider (Long Term Part Timers)",
  "description": "<p>Flex Logistics is a fast-growing Healthcare Supply Chain as a Service startup in Singapore.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><em>For more details, please visit our website </em>https://www.flexlogistics.sg/<em>.</em></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Description:</strong> A Logistics Specialist (Rider) is responsible for efficiently transporting goods and packages from one location to another using motorcycle. This role requires strong time management skills, <u><strong>able to work in a structured team environment</strong></u>, able to work under pressure and the ability to navigate through traffic and various terrains. Most importantly, strong customer service, <u><strong>there will be high degree of engagement with customers and what we deliver is quality.</strong></u></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<p>1) Island wide collection and delivery of spectacles and lens (very light items)</p>\n<p>2) Two waves per day, 12.30pm and 4.30pm</p>\n<p>3) Start and return to Bendemeer daily</p>\n<p>3) Our areas are clustered</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<p>1) Possess Class 2B valid driving license.</p>\n<p>2) Possess own motorbike with box.</p>\n<p>3) Valid commercial motorcycle insurance.</p>\n<p>4) Familiar with Singapore road.</p>\n<p>5) Familiar with using mobile application for job assignment, POD etc.</p>\n<p>6) Customer service oriented, good working attitude, interpersonal and communication skills.</p>\n<p>7) Collaborative mindset that can excel in a structured team environment.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Part Time Rider :<br>\n<br>\n<strong>1) Monday to Friday(11.30am to 7pm) -</strong> Supplier will be paid a daily fee of <strong>$80.00</strong> per day for two waves of collection and delivery runs</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>2) Saturday (12.30pm to 6pm) -</strong> Supplier will be paid a daily fee of <strong>$100.00</strong> per day for one waves of collection and delivery runs</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>3) Sunday and Public Holiday (12pm onwards, OTOT) -</strong> Supplier will be paid a daily fee of <strong>$100.00</strong> per day for one wave of collection and delivery run.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Additional incentives for commitment - $20.00 per day</strong>, for completion of full week without fail. These additional incentives will not apply for any lapses in any working day of the week. It is not considered a lapse if there is a Public Holiday within the week,</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>**As we recieved many applicants for the role, we will <strong>priortize riders that can commit to Mon-FRI schedule.**</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>ONLY APPLY THROUGH CAREERFUTURE OR EMAIL yiting.liew@flexlogistics.sg or apply via https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1nRoqwPZAx6z5CStmsRQX2j3J-J-erR6S3MN084_XR_E/edit?ts=64abb4b0</strong></p>\n<p><strong>(WE DO NOT POST OUR JOB IN ANY OTHER PLATFORMS)</strong></p>",
